l2Norm(Matrix) - 类 中的方法artiano.core.structure.Matrix
Calculate the l2-norm between current matrix and specified matrix x Given matrix x and y, the method to calculate the l2-norm is:
l2-norm=sqrt{sum[x(i, j) - y(i, j)]}
